{"tid":711080,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★瑞銀警告亞洲股市有機累冧30%   06月21日(四) 15:44","createTime":"2018-06-21T09:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T11:13:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b0b6d172aaab7577c524125bbb5079749fad3b","tid":711080,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，瑞銀發表報告指出，亞洲股市正在對中美貿易戰再度升溫、拖累企業盈利可能倒退20%而定價。該行警告，一旦發生全面貿易戰，亞洲股市恐由今年1月頂部累冧30%。<br />\n<br />\n該行指出，很明顯的是市場仍未就更負面的結果定價。<br />\n<br />\n回顧香港恒生指數歷史最高為2018年1月29日所創的33,484點；歷史最高收市點數則是1月26日所創的33,154點。若瑞銀的預測在港股應驗，恒指恐要跌至23,000點水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180621/bkn-20180621154444456-0621_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180621%2Fbkn-20180621154444456-0621_00842_001.html&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e03d5a67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180621/bkn-20180621154444456-0621_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b65c6a988bc6c009da906b2f9cad8aacbfbf2a38","tid":711080,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6cc2ce20494a50497a8170b5082772733f87c0","tid":711080,"uid":44783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:14:32.000Z","msg":"係就快啦<br />\n講左幾廿次"},{"pid":"0bf05dae396995df1db83db37c5ebe6b52ffeecc","tid":711080,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0b0b6d172aaab7577c524125bbb5079749fad3b","tid":711080,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09: